        "title": "Boum Garden",
        "description": "Connects Home Assistant directly to the Boum IoT REST API. You can also select the tank size during setup. To calculate litres, add the sensor distance when the tank is empty and full. Note: “local” is a local development/proxy endpoint according to the Boum CLI docs, not automatically the plant device IP.",
